songs.title: Hollywood
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Did I stutter when I told you to get away from me?

[Verse 1]
Your white jacket makes you feel so awesome
Your white jacket makes you look so handsome
Your big fat wallet looks like your big fat head
Don't want another drink, want to go to bed

[Chorus]
Hollywood, this song's for you
Hollywood, I don't really like you
Hollywood, this song's for you
Hollywood (get away from me)

[Verse 2]
If Los Angeles fell into the sea
I would miss my couch, it is very velvety
And like one person, but mostly
I would feel very sorry for the fishies

[Chorus]
Hollywood, this song's for you
Hollywood, I don't really like you
Hollywood, this song's for you
Hollywood (get away from me)
